text: John E. Weidenboerner House is a historic home located at St. Mary's in Elk County, Pennsylvania. It was built in 1881 in the Italianate style. Note: This includes and It is located within the St. Marys Historic District. It was added to the National Register of Historic Places in 1992. ==Gallery== John E.
